{"tid":1408382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對峙無意思 掉雞蛋啦又無殺傷力","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T03:43:57.000Z","uid":24265,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6fea539f9b53de42055b9a41b0f626e3fdf010f4","tid":1408382,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:10:17.000Z","msg":"到開拖時候先自己發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日唔該大家一齊買雞蛋餵狗呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又平又正 佢地要朝早挨撚凌晨呀<br />\n著撚住果套野 臭撚到仆街<br />\n<br />\n打怪用魔攻減防先啦 消耗戰黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日一人N蛋餵狗</span><br />\n見到就開始掉 唔好等啦 行過就掉 無晒就再去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又平又抵屌<br />\n<br />\n聽日要大量蛋 大規模咁餵<br />\n和理非唔敢掉lego 雞蛋敢啦掛 0殺傷力<br />\n<br />\n遠敢既 幻彩詠香江 雞蛋 雙管齊下<br />\n<br />\n幫手推 聽日3罷 一齊去買 低成本<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高效益</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫手推 推到一人一盒 推到常態<br />\n最緊要係和理非都可以一齊餵狗！！"},{"pid":"159ef75f054f638b18ec630a6548ae927ea0d212","tid":1408382,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:10:55.000Z","msg":"我要餵狗！！"},{"pid":"ea7f221d2affb03a8f378957b24b73eacd47467e","tid":1408382,"uid":24265,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:12:52.000Z","msg":"樓主咪on9啦 玩弄食物好折墮"},{"pid":"6d36beaa7e0b16624ec09976ac69401ecc43cbca","tid":1408382,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c342c09e191343b098ef112ec77a1e23d18c0eb9","tid":1408382,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"幫手推啦ching"},{"pid":"0b2491c50c98aae5d853d7e1ac2d90b2d2826ce7","tid":1408382,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-